Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.69,0:00:29.95,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}迷失於悖論
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.91,0:00:33.37,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}仇恨灼燒我的靈魂
